title: Adobe CS6 Master Collection
description:
This special distribution of this software suite contains a handcrafted crack assistant tool developed in C# by me. The source code to it is included in this torrent. This includes these programs:

Acrobat X Pro
Audition CS6
Bridge CS6
Dreamweaver CS6
Extension Manager CS6
Fireworks CS6
Flash Builder 4.6
Flash CS6
Illustrator CS6
InDesign CS6
Photoshop CS6
Prelude CS6
After Effects CS6
Encore CS6
Illustrator CS6
Media Encoder CS6
Premiere Pro CS6
SpeedGrade CS6

I spent quite a bit of time making the Crack Assistant not only to make it easier for me but for anyone who wants this. Enjoy!
